FuncDef: This command removes the specified leases in the specified local DHCPv6 server.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the prefix of the leases to be removed.
Specifies the type of the lease to be removed. Values-pd, slaac, wan-host.
Specifies the state of the lease to be removed. Values-advertised, remove-pending, held, internal, internal-orphan, internal-offered.
Removes all leases of specified type or state.
